read_metric_html_package(25.10)                read_metric_html_package(25.10)

Name
       read_metric_html_package  - Overwrites the HTML for report_metric -for-
       mat vivid and the vivid page configuration  (accessible  via  read_met-
       ric_config/write_metric_config)  with  the  contents from the specified
       filename

Syntax
        read_metric_html_package

       [-help]

       filename

       Overwrites the HTML for report_metric -format vivid and the vivid  page
       configuration  (accessible  via read_metric_config/write_metric_config)
       with the contents from the specified filename.

Parameters
       <filename>
              Specifies the name of the file from where the tool will read the
              metric package.

              If the specified <filename> is not a supported format, the  tool
              will give an error message that the file format is invalid.

              Data_type: string, required

       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for each read_metric_html_package parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man read_metric_html_package

Related Information
              * read_metric_config

              * report_metric

              * write_metric_config

